### Update an event
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/events/<event-id>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "churchId": "church-1",
  "name": "Culto Atualizado",
  "description": "Descrição atualizada",
  "startDatetime": "2025-12-01T10:00:00Z",
  "endDatetime": "2025-12-01T12:00:00Z",
  "location": "Nova Localização",
  "createdBy": "admin"
}

### Delete an event
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/events/<event-id>
